The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence in cellular networks, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the technical challenges of deploying AI in cellular networks, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the need for robustness and performance, which are topics in control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
